  "texts": [
    "The next section focuses on AI's role in influencing patient self-care and behavior change, considering the ethical implications of such interventions.",
    "Finally, the paper discusses the impact of generative AI on the patient-physician relationship, weighing both the threats and enhancements to this critical dynamic.",
    "The review concludes with a discussion of the key findings, their implications for clinical practice, and suggestions for future research.",
    "Review MethodsA search of the literature was conducted using multiple databases, including PubMed, MEDLINE, Scopus, and Google Scholar, with the aim of identifying relevant studies that discuss the impact of generative AI on patient learning and the patient-physician relationship.",
    "The search was conducted between October 7, 2024, and November 10, 2024."
